What is Amazon Renewed?

Amazon Renewed is your trusted destination for products that are inspected, tested, and refurbished as necessary to be fully functional.

Quality that you can afford

Amazon Renewed products offer an affordable option so you can save on the brands that you love.

Products you can trust

All products have been professionally inspected, tested, cleaned, and refurbished as necessary by Amazon-qualified suppliers.

Purchases with an impact

Your Amazon Renewed purchase extends the lifetime of this product and reduces electronic waste.

Trusted coverage

Your purchase is eligible for Amazon Renewed coverage in conjunction with Amazon's Return Policy and the A-to-z Guarantee.

What should I expect to receive with my Amazon Renewed purchase?

All Amazon Renewed purchases will come with accessories equivalent to those that shipped in the box when new. These items may not be original but will be compatible and fully functional. Amazon Renewed products will be packaged in either original packaging or in a new and clean cardboard box.

Product description

This pre-owned or refurbished product has been professionally inspected and tested to work and look like new. How a product becomes part of Amazon Renewed, your destination for pre-owned, refurbished products: A customer buys a new product and returns it or trades it in for a newer or different model. That product is inspected and tested to work and look like new by Amazon-qualified suppliers. Then, the product is sold as an Amazon Renewed product on Amazon. If not satisfied with the purchase, renewed products are eligible for replacement or refund under the Amazon Renewed Guarantee.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Amazon Customer
4 Stars
Very pleased
The phone, together with the accessories to go with it, arrived promptly. While there were no set-up instructions included, doing so was fairly simple. All updates, together with the transfer from my old Samsung, was completed in about 2 hours.The phone was a refurb, so you'd expect some wear, and you can see in the pictures, there are 2 "rough" spots that are completely covered by the Spigen case I also bought. So, the scratches are a non-issue. The case back and the screen are in great condition.My only complaint would be with the USB-C cable provided. The adaptor says "Adaptive Fast Charging" but when I charge the phone it says "slow charging, for faster charging use a supported charger. Make sure the cable isn't damaged" (see picture). So, I switched the cable for the braided one I already had (see picture) - now just over an hour to fully charge. If I didn't have the extra cable, the poor quality cable would have ruined an otherwise good experience - take note Amazon Renewed Store. (lost 1 star here)

4.0 out of 5 stars Great phone. Battery okay. Why an iphone charging cable?
Reviewed in Canada on September 14, 2023
Verified Purchase
This phone is fantastic for the price. It is zippy between and in app usage. The screen is beautiful. The condition of the phone is impeccable. The battery is supposed to be a minimum 80% of factory capacity, but I wonder. Perhaps my previous budget phones had more robust batteries, but I would expect better. When using throughout the day I am wanting to plug it in when I get home. Otherwise: the phone is great and I will likely buy used from this seller again.
But why did they send it in a random box with an IPHONE CHARGING CABLE?! That makes no sense. I had cords from previous phones, but if I am spending just over $300 (CDN) on a phone shouldn't I at least get one cord to charge it with? Odd mistake to make, but still a great phone.
